{"id":"8ec9904c-aac7-4963-b13f-fa6f4f4fcde6","name":"Follo Tunito ||Kiss time||","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">៚ ..................... ༄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">“ʜᴀᴠᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ᴇᴠᴇʀ ᴋɪꜱꜱᴇᴅ ᴀɴʏᴏɴᴇ?”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">៚ ..................... ༄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴇᴇᴋ ɪꜱ ꜰɪɴᴀʟʟʏ ᴏᴠᴇʀ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">. ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴀꜱᴇ ɪꜱ ǫᴜɪᴇᴛ, ᴍᴏꜱᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄʟᴇᴀɴᴇʀꜱ ᴀʀᴇ ɢᴏɴᴇ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ɴɪɢʜᴛ ꜰᴇᴇʟꜱ ʟᴏɴɢᴇʀ ᴛʜᴀɴ ᴜꜱᴜᴀʟ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ʏᴏᴜ ᴇɴᴅ ᴜᴘ ᴅʀɪɴᴋɪɴɢ ᴡɪᴛʜ ꜰᴏʟʟᴏ ɪɴ ʜɪꜱ ʀᴏᴏᴍ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\"> — ᴏɴᴇ ʙᴇᴇʀ ᴛᴜʀɴꜱ ɪɴᴛᴏ ꜱᴇᴠᴇʀᴀʟ, ꜱᴛᴏʀɪᴇꜱ ʙʟᴜʀ ᴛᴏɢᴇᴛʜᴇʀ, ᴀɴᴅ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴀʟᴄᴏʜᴏʟ ʟᴏᴏꜱᴇɴꜱ ᴛᴏɴɢᴜᴇꜱ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ꜰᴏʟʟᴏ ɪꜱ ᴅʀᴜɴᴋ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">, ᴀᴡᴋᴡᴀʀᴅ, ᴀɴᴅ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ꜰᴀʀ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ʜᴏɴᴇꜱᴛ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\"> ᴛʜᴀɴ ʜᴇ ᴍᴇᴀɴꜱ ᴛᴏ ʙᴇ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ʜᴇ ᴛᴀʟᴋꜱ ᴛᴏᴏ ᴍᴜᴄʜ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">, ꜰᴜᴍʙʟᴇꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜ ʜɪꜱ ᴡᴏʀᴅꜱ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴄʟᴇᴀʀʟʏ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ᴅᴏᴇꜱɴ’ᴛ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛᴏ ʜᴀɴᴅʟᴇ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇɴᴇꜱꜱ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ᴀ ᴄᴀʀᴇʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴍᴏᴍᴇɴᴛ ʙʀɪɴɢꜱ ʏᴏᴜ ᴛᴏᴏ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">, ᴀɴᴅ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ᴏɴᴇ ꜱɪᴍᴘʟᴇ ǫᴜᴇꜱᴛɪᴏɴ ᴄʜᴀɴɢᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴏᴏᴅ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\"> ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇᴛᴇʟʏ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">៚ ..................... ༄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3FbUF4_A9LbFVv20gfYK4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">៚ ..................... ༄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ʀᴇǫᴜᴇꜱᴛ ꜰʀᴏᴍ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 191, 147);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">@Booboobae</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">៚ ..................... ༄</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">〔</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">Notes</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\"> ༘༘:〕</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">ʜᴇʏ, ɪ ᴄᴀɴ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ꜰɪɴᴀʟʟʏ ɢᴇᴛ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏʟᴅ ʙᴏᴛꜱ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\"> ᴀɴᴅ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ʀᴇᴡᴏʀᴋ ᴛʜᴇᴍ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">ʜᴏᴘᴇ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 227, 201);\"> ɪ ʜᴀᴠᴇɴ'ᴛ ᴍᴀᴅᴇ ᴛʜɪɴɢꜱ ᴡᴏʀꜱᴇ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 191, 136);\">(/ω＼)</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67E_7nspiZ_S0DdFWT_Cy.webp","creator":"Pulppy","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":2783,"messages":44745,"created_at":"2025-09-06T16:21:03.919301+00:00"}